high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter in front of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter, in front of the sink on the left.
Move over to the counter on the right side of the sink.
Cut the tomato near the corner of the counter into slices.
Step back from the counter and turn so that you are facing the bottom cabinets and dishwasher.
Place the knife in the left side of the cabinet to the right of the dishwasher.
Turn back to the counter top to the right of the sink where the cut tomato is.
Pick up one of the slices of tomato on the counter top.
Move over to the small sink on your left.
Place the tomato slice in the small sink on the left, turn the water on, rinse off the tomato slice, turn the water off, and remove the tomato slice from the sink.
Move back over to the counter to top to the right of the sink.
Place the slice of tomato on the counter, in front of the sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the cabinet and a clean tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right to face the sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter in front of the leftmost sink.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the counter on the left where the tomato is.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn around and face the dishwasher.
Put the knife inside the cabinet that is to the right of the dishwasher.
Go forward, go to the left to the counter where the tomato is.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right to face the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink, rinse it off then pick it back up.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the left to face the sink.
Put the tomato on the counter in front of the rightmost sink.
anns.task_desc: Put clean tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and stop at the sink
Grab the knife that is in front of the sink
Move slightly to the right
Slice the tomato on the counter
Back up and face the cabinets on the bottom on the right
Put the knife in the bottom right cabinet
Turn left and stand in front of the sink
Grab a slice of tomato off of the counter
Move slightly to the left and stop at the sink
Wash the sliced tomato in the sink and then take it out
Move slightly to the right
Put the sliced tomato in front of the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting clean sliced tomato down in front of the sink
